{
  "name": "mcp-sophon",
  "version": "0.1.0",
  "description": "Honest token economics for MCP agents. Deterministic context layer: prompt compression, conversation memory, code navigation, file delta, output compression. Single Rust binary, zero ML, reproducible benchmarks. ~67% session savings; ties mem0 on LOCOMO at sub-second vs 8.7 min; beats LLMLingua-2 on structured prompts by ~10pts at ~35x lower latency.",
